This paper is likely to belong to the Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI) sub-category as it studies the dynamics of emotional contagion in social media. It may also belong to the Social Networks (cs.SN) sub-category as it analyzes the behavior of individuals in a social network. The paper also involves data analysis and modeling, which could place it in the Software Engineering (cs.SE) or Cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-categories. Additionally, the study involves ethical concerns, which could place it in the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
